{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":946,"text":"I'm here to show you"},{"time":2670,"text":"how something you can't see can be so much fun to look at."},{"time":6371,"text":"You're about to experience a new, available"},{"time":10174,"text":"and exciting technology that's going to make us rethink"},{"time":13154,"text":"how we waterproof our lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":15282,"text":"What I have here is a cinder block"},{"time":18002,"text":"that we've coated half with a nanotechnology spray"},{"time":20498,"text":"that can be applied to almost any material."},{"time":23090,"text":"It's called Ultra-Ever Dry,"},{"time":25427,"text":"and when you apply it to any material,"},{"time":27853,"text":"it turns into a superhydrophobic shield."},{"time":30958,"text":"So this is a cinder block, uncoated,"},{"time":33484,"text":"and you can see that it's porous, it absorbs water."},{"time":37785,"text":"Not anymore."},{"time":40439,"text":"Porous, nonporous."}]},{"cues":[{"time":44666,"text":"So what's superhydrophobic?"},{"time":47418,"text":"Superhydrophobic is how we measure"},{"time":49911,"text":"a drop of water on a surface."},{"time":52393,"text":"The rounder it is, the more hydrophobic it is,"},{"time":54793,"text":"and if it's really round, it's superhydrophobic."},{"time":57721,"text":"A freshly waxed car, the water molecules slump"},{"time":60667,"text":"to about 90 degrees."},{"time":63607,"text":"A windshield coating is going to give you about 110 degrees."},{"time":66695,"text":"But what you're seeing here is 160 to 175 degrees,"},{"time":69476,"text":"and anything over 150 is superhydrophobic."},{"time":73488,"text":"So as part of the demonstration,"},{"time":75037,"text":"what I have is a pair of gloves,"},{"time":77551,"text":"and we've coated one of the gloves"},{"time":79719,"text":"with the nanotechnology coating,"},{"time":82423,"text":"and let's see if you can tell which one,"},{"time":84223,"text":"and I'll give you a hint."}]},{"cues":[{"time":91280,"text":"Did you guess the one that was dry?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":95904,"text":"When you have nanotechnology and nanoscience,"},{"time":100606,"text":"what's occurred is that we're able to now"},{"time":103278,"text":"look at atoms and molecules and actually control them"},{"time":105791,"text":"for great benefits."},{"time":108223,"text":"And we're talking really small here."},{"time":110222,"text":"The way you measure nanotechnology is in nanometers,"},{"time":112494,"text":"and one nanometer is a billionth of a meter,"},{"time":116321,"text":"and to put some scale to that,"},{"time":117968,"text":"if you had a nanoparticle that was one nanometer thick,"},{"time":121274,"text":"and you put it side by side, and you had 50,000 of them,"},{"time":124089,"text":"you'd be the width of a human hair."},{"time":126937,"text":"So very small, but very useful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":129945,"text":"And it's not just water that this works with."},{"time":132849,"text":"It's a lot of water-based materials like concrete,"},{"time":135600,"text":"water-based paint,"},{"time":137769,"text":"mud,"},{"time":139417,"text":"and also some refined oils as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":147216,"text":"You can see the difference."}]},{"cues":[{"time":151605,"text":"Moving onto the next demonstration,"},{"time":153095,"text":"we've taken a pane of glass and we've coated the outside of it,"},{"time":155389,"text":"we've framed it with the nanotechnology coating,"},{"time":158639,"text":"and we're going to pour this green-tinted water inside the middle,"},{"time":162414,"text":"and you're going to see, it's going to spread out on glass"},{"time":164375,"text":"like you'd normally think it would,"},{"time":165925,"text":"except when it hits the coating, it stops,"},{"time":169519,"text":"and I can't even coax it to leave."},{"time":173304,"text":"It's that afraid of the water."}]},{"cues":[{"time":174907,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":178627,"text":"So what's going on here? What's happening?"},{"time":180379,"text":"Well, the surface of the spray coating"},{"time":183667,"text":"is actually filled with nanoparticles"},{"time":185428,"text":"that form a very rough and craggly surface."},{"time":187502,"text":"You'd think it'd be smooth, but it's actually not."},{"time":190091,"text":"And it has billions of interstitial spaces,"},{"time":192862,"text":"and those spaces, along with the nanoparticles,"},{"time":195971,"text":"reach up and grab the air molecules,"},{"time":198323,"text":"and cover the surface with air."},{"time":200386,"text":"It's an umbrella of air all across it,"},{"time":203131,"text":"and that layer of air is what the water hits,"},{"time":205771,"text":"the mud hits, the concrete hits, and it glides right off."},{"time":208819,"text":"So if I put this inside this water here,"},{"time":210835,"text":"you can see a silver reflective coating around it,"},{"time":214955,"text":"and that silver reflective coating"},{"time":216411,"text":"is the layer of air that's protecting the water"},{"time":218682,"text":"from touching the paddle, and it's dry."}]},{"cues":[{"time":225340,"text":"So what are the applications?"},{"time":227837,"text":"I mean, many of you right now are probably going through your head."},{"time":230285,"text":"Everyone that sees this gets excited, and says,"},{"time":231783,"text":"\"Oh, I could use it for this and this and this.\""},{"time":233712,"text":"The applications in a general sense"},{"time":235774,"text":"could be anything that's anti-wetting."},{"time":238604,"text":"We've certainly seen that today."},{"time":240869,"text":"It could be anything that's anti-icing,"},{"time":243453,"text":"because if you don't have water, you don't have ice."},{"time":246908,"text":"It could be anti-corrosion."},{"time":249180,"text":"No water, no corrosion."},{"time":251206,"text":"It could be anti-bacterial."},{"time":253404,"text":"Without water, the bacteria won't survive."},{"time":256113,"text":"And it could be things that need to be self-cleaning as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":261629,"text":"So imagine how something like this"},{"time":265501,"text":"could help revolutionize your field of work."},{"time":269622,"text":"And I'm going to leave you with one last demonstration,"},{"time":272021,"text":"but before I do that, I would like to say thank you,"},{"time":274622,"text":"and think small."},{"time":285098,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":292646,"text":"It's going to happen. Wait for it. Wait for it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":297035,"text":"Chris Anderson: You guys didn't hear about us cutting out the Design from TED? (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":301817,"text":"[Two minutes later...]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":303567,"text":"He ran into all sorts of problems in terms of managing the medical research part."},{"time":306251,"text":"It's happening!"},{"time":308814,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}